OL,3,CLionel Messi: Crazy to face Lamine
OL,4,CYamal in World Cup final after baby
OL,5,Cphoto
OL,7,FArgentina captain Lionel Messi says it
OL,8,Fis "crazy" to be preparing to face
OL,9,FSpain star Lamine Yamal in the World
OL,10,FCup final after being photographed
OL,11,Fwith him as a baby.
OL,13,FThe pair's unlikely connection dates
OL,14,Fback to 2007 when a five-month-old
OL,15,FYamal was held by Messi after his
OL,16,Fparents won a charity photoshoot in
OL,17,FBarcelona.
OL,26,@pD@DOUpD@JO]
