OL,3,CLionel Messi: Crazy to face Lamine
OL,4,CYamal in World Cup final after baby
OL,5,Cphoto
OL,7,FWorld Cup holders Argentina, who
OL,8,Fdefeated England 2-1 in the semi-
OL,9,Ffinals, will take on European
OL,10,Fchampions Spain in Sunday's final in
OL,11,FNew Jersey.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FSpeaking to Messi during a news
OL,19,Fconference in New York, NFL's Tom
OL,20,FBrady described the photos as "very
OL,21,Fprophetic".
