PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784431086
OL,3,CLionel Messi: Crazy to face Lamine
OL,4,CYamal in World Cup final after baby
OL,5,Cphoto
OL,7,FMessi said: "That photo is incredible.
OL,8,FThe fact that we're both playing in
OL,9,Fthe World Cup now is crazy."
OL,11,FYamal made his Barcelona debut at the
OL,12,Fage of 15 in 2023 before inheriting
OL,13,Fthe number 10 shirt previously worn by
OL,14,FMessi.
OL,16,FFollowing Euro 2024 glory with Spain,
OL,17,Fthe 19-year-old could become the
OL,18,Fyoungest player to win the European
OL,19,FChampionship and the World Cup.
OL,26,@oD@MOUqD@\O]
