PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784431086
OL,3,CLionel Messi: Crazy to face Lamine
OL,4,CYamal in World Cup final after baby
OL,5,Cphoto
OL,7,F"He's one of the best in the world
OL,8,Fright now," said 39-year-old Messi,
OL,9,Fnow of Inter Miami.
OL,11,F"I wish him luck because his success
OL,12,Fwill be Barcelona's success.
OL,14,F"We'll try to keep him from playing at
OL,15,Fhis best. Spain has a great team, not
OL,16,Fjust him.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@KO]sD@AOUvD@AOU
