PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784431086
OL,3,CLionel Messi: Crazy to face Lamine
OL,4,CYamal in World Cup final after baby
OL,5,Cphoto
OL,7,F"He's a tremendous player ` a global
OL,8,Fstar. He's 19 years old and has his
OL,9,Fwhole career ahead of him. I wish him
OL,10,Fthe best, but we'll give it our all to
OL,11,Fensure he doesn't become champion this
OL,12,Ftime."
